<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>310</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kisau kido di'n! dogal a nai tai,
 Puonlap dawmsang un, Lalpa di'n;
 Kigalvan un, dettak in ding chiet un!
 A thu thiengtho chuh mangin, pang un!

[V2]
 Tho un, sepaih! Lal puonlap nuoi achun,
 Kisau unla, A thu gensawn un;
 Malam zuon un! Hossana! ti'n sam un,
 Krista chuh sepaih puipa ahi.

[V3]
 2. I galteu tuok di'n malam I zuon zel,
 Panmun I het chun zo hitiu;
 Phaw leh puonlap thieng taka vawp zingin,
 Thudik a pangte, puk ngei puoi tiu.

[V4]
 3. Aw micheng Pathien, ka sapnau ngaiin,
 Na zahngaih na'n ei panpih in;
 Galzawh ahih a kidona beih tieng,
 Na ma achun Lallukhuk khung kau.</lyrics>
<title>SOUND THE BATTLE CRY</title>
</song>